videos.title: ElGrandeToto  - Live from OLM Souissi | SALGOAT Tour | Mawazine 2025
videos.description:
ElGrandeToto set Mawazine 2025 ablaze as the first Moroccan rapper to rock the OLM Souissi stage on June 28! With his trilingual flow and bangers like “Mghayer” and “Blue Love,” he hyped up 400,000 fans before passing the mic to Lil Baby. Don’t miss this epic vibe—watch the concert now and dive into the raw energy of the Maghrebi rap king!
